		"txt":"{\"instruction\":[],\"productName\":\"Monitoring\",\"label\":[{\"TitleName\":\"Try Now\",\"TitleUrl\":\"https://cms-console.jdcloud.com/overviewMonitor\"}],\"desc\":\"The Monitoring can monitor the users' JD Cloud resources and raising alarms, monitor and display various indicators and raise alarm over the monitoring indicators. It will send alarm notifications via SMS, E-mail, etc., and provide users with current alarm status and alarm history. The Monitoring helps customers master the resource usage status, performance and operation on JD Cloud; and the alarm service enables customers to make timely response for stable operation of the application.\",\"iconUrl\":\"Óùê\",\"imageUrl\":\"//jdcloud-portal.oss.cn-north-1.jcloudcs.com/www.jcloud.com/1992e773-64de-4733-92dd-2fd14fe3f29f20181115172929.svg\",\"middleClstag\":\"Products|keycount|MiddleContentSec|11\",\"sectionClstag\":\"Products|keycount|SectionBannerSec|11\"}",
