	{
		"txt":"[{\"proGood\":\"Simple and Easy to Use\",\"proName\":\"There is no need to specially apply for subscription of Monitoring. Once any JD Cloud resource supported by Monitoring is purchased, corresponding monitoring data can be viewed. The alarm function can guide configuration in steps, providing simple and time-saving process.\",\"showShade\":false},{\"proGood\":\"Real-time and Reliable\",\"proName\":\"The original sampling data can be reported in real time and cloud service can be monitored in real time. When monitoring indicator of cloud service reaches the threshold set by the alarm rules, emails and SMS will be automatically sent. Users can know business operation conditions immediately and improve business availability.\"},{\"showShade\":false,\"imageUrl\":\"\",\"proGood\":\"Flexible and Diversified\",\"proName\":\"The alarm rules support customized alarm levels. When resource monitoring indicators reach the threshold, the alarm level will be automatically matched. Meanwhile, alarm callback can also been conducted through the alarm mode, so that users can set up the intelligent program processing alarm.\"},{\"showShade\":false,\"imageUrl\":\"\",\"proGood\":\"View Enrichment\",\"proName\":\"Dashboard supports cross-region and cross-product management and monitoring graph. There are three types of display, including schedule, statement and TOPN graph and a variety of operation methods including zooming and data export, meeting the demands for visualization and troubleshooting under different scenarios.\"}]",
		"id":37
	},
	{
		"txt":"[{\"funcContent\":[{\"funcP\":\"After purchasing and using the JD Cloud service supported by the Monitoring, users can easily view the running status of their products and the status of the monitoring indicators in Monitoring pages corresponding to products. \",\"funcTitle\":\"Simple and Easy-to-use Function\"},{\"funcTitle\":\"Complete Monitoring Products\",\"funcP\":\"Monitoring types cover computation, network, storage, database, middleware and big data service and support more than 30 monitoring products.\"},{\"funcTitle\":\"Open API\",\"funcP\":\"Provide OpenAPI API, so that users can customize business demands as per demands.\"}],\"funcName\":\"Resource Monitoring\"},{\"funcContent\":[{\"funcP\":\"With this function, users can monitor business indicators which they concern and report collected monitoring data to Monitoring. Then, Monitoring will process data and trigger alarms as per results.\",\"funcTitle\":\"Provide the function of customizing and reporting monitoring indicator and data\"},{\"funcTitle\":\"Support aggregation dimension search monitoring graph and configuration alarm\",\"funcP\":\"Provide monitoring graph search function; users can search monitoring graph dimension and statistic method for monitoring data statistics; meanwhile, alarm rules also support monitoring aggregation of monitoring data according to the dimension prescribed by users.\"}],\"funcName\":\"Custom Metric Monitoring\"},{\"funcContent\":[{\"funcP\":\"For resource monitoring, users can appoint existing instance configuration alarms and also can make configuration as per tags; after resources are added under any tag, new resources can be automatically obtained without changing any rules; policy notification forms are flexible and diversified, including: SMS, email and alarm callback, which can be appointed; and notification period and notification time can also be customized.\",\"funcTitle\":\"Flexible and Convenient Alarm Policy Setting\"},{\"funcTitle\":\"Create and update alarm rules quickly with the template\",\"funcP\":\"Users can use default alarm templates provided by JD Cloud or customized alarm templates created by themselves to rapidly create alarm rules for cloud resources. Meanwhile, after alarm templates are changed, association rules will come into force immediately.\"}],\"funcName\":\"Alarm Service\"}]",
